  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knock down coins one after another and obtain the treasures of the gods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't miss out when gold rains down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Score Attack]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn as many coins as possible within the time limit and aim for a high spot on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Endless]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play for as long as you like without a time limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your coin count will persist between tries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranking]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn a rank for both Score Attack and Endless modes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the highest coin count with players worldwide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play together with up to 4 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone or together, aim for your next high score!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knock down coins one after another and obtain the treasures of the gods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't miss out when gold rains down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Score Attack]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn as many coins as possible within the time limit and aim for a high spot on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Endless]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play for as long as you like without a time limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your coin count will persist between tries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranking]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn a rank for both Score Attack and Endless modes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the highest coin count with players worldwide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play together with up to 4 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone or together, aim for your next high score!</p>",
